<main id="content" class="content"> <header> <h1 class="title">Real Riches</h1>
 <p class="subtitle" role="doc-subtitle">May 07, 2017 00:00</p>
</header> <blockquote class="bigquote">
 <p>
A propensity to hope and joy is real riches; one to fear and sorrow, real poverty.
</p>
</blockquote>

 <p class="bigquote">
David Hume,  <i>Essays, Moral, Political, and Literary</i>, Part I, Essay 18
</p>


